        "description": "<p>WP Basic Authentication is a plugin for protected your development WordPress site like .htpasswd and support Docker and Kubernetes (K8s)<\/p>\n<p>Features:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Easy for setting Basic Authentication<\/li>\n<li>Basic Authentication works like .htpasswd<\/li>\n<li>Protected development website or demo website without .htpasswd<\/li>\n<li>Support Docker and Kubernetes (K8s)<\/li>\n<li>The plugin is lightweight.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Upload <code>wp-basic-authentication.zip<\/code> to the install plugin page<\/li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the &#8216;Plugins&#8217; menu in WordPress<\/li>\n<li>Go to <em>Authentication<\/em> in the left-hand menu to start setting the plugin<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n",
        "faq": "\n<dt id='how%20to%20setting%20the%20plugin%3F'>\nHow to setting the plugin?\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p>Go to <em>Authentication<\/em> in the left-hand menu to start setting the plugin<\/p>\n<\/p>\n<dt id='how%20to%20disable%20authentication%20if%20i%20forgot%20the%20credentials'>\nHow to disable Authentication if I forgot the credentials\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p>Rename or delete &#8216;wp-basic-authentication&#8217; directory in plugins directory via FTP or commend line<\/p>\n<\/p>\n\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>1.0.3<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tested up to WordPress 6.5<\/li>\n<li>Separate protected frontend and wp-login page<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.2<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tested up to WordPress 6.1.1<\/li>\n<li>Add Tip me on ko-fi<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tested up to WordPress 5.8.1<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.0<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial Release<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n",
        "screenshots": "<ol><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/wp-basic-authentication\/assets\/screenshot-1.png?rev=2384114\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/wp-basic-authentication\/assets\/screenshot-1.png?rev=2384114\" alt=\"Basic Authentication dialog\"><\/a><p>Basic Authentication dialog<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/wp-basic-authentication\/assets\/screenshot-2.png?rev=2384116\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/wp-basic-authentication\/assets\/screenshot-2.png?rev=2384116\" alt=\"Screenshot of the menu page for Featured Posts Setting page.\"><\/a><p>Screenshot of the menu page for Featured Posts Setting page.<\/p><\/li><\/ol>",
        "reviews": "<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Still working perfectly<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/jcollier\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/4be6e20a7ba29f40e83fb7db73b2ea7f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/4be6e20a7ba29f40e83fb7db73b2ea7f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/jcollier\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Jay Collier <small>(jcollier)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">October 4, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">This plugin is still working perfectly, just as described.<br \/><br \/>(Can you update the compatibility version? It shows this on install: \"Warning:\u00a0This plugin\u00a0has not been tested\u00a0with your current version of WordPress.\")<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Works perfectly<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/lighthaus205\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/697687b24671a55164038814865fd932?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/697687b24671a55164038814865fd932?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/lighthaus205\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">lighthaus205<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">October 4, 2022<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">Works just as expected.\nThanks a lot!<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Very Nicely Done<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/brokercarrier\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/dd6c9d7ede907f09cc73d58a80618ec3?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/dd6c9d7ede907f09cc73d58a80618ec3?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/brokercarrier\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">brokercarrier<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 5, 2021<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">This plugin perfectly reproduces the functionality of .htpasswd on Apache. We needed a solution like this for a website that is running on OpenLiteSpeed, and it works perfectly. Thank you!<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great for basic privacy<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/epymetheus\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/775ea482e3fc8c2ef8278f8fc6146593?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/775ea482e3fc8c2ef8278f8fc6146593?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/epymetheus\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Adam Blodgett <small>(epymetheus)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">May 21, 2021<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">Plugin does what it promises: easy and quick HTTP-like authentication. Easy to install and use.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n"
